---
// src/components/Packages.astro
---

<section id="packages" class="packages">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Work With Us</h2>
      <p>Scoped engagements with clear deliverables</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tiers-grid">
      <div class="service-tier service-tier--free">
        <div class="tier-top">
          <h3>Free Consult</h3>
          <p class="pricing">Free</p>
          <p class="timing">1 hour</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-body">
          <ul>
            <li>1-on-1 conversation with Ben Medcalf</li>
            <li>Assess fit for AI, graph databases, or automation</li>
            <li>Actionable recommendation: build, wait, or look elsewhere</li>
            <li>Rough scope and effort estimate if there's a fit</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Figuring out if we're the right partner — zero risk.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="https://calendar.app.google/jzac8cPcXKKtnVQ39" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="tier-cta">Book a Free Hour</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-tier">
        <div class="tier-top">
          <h3>Discovery Sprint</h3>
          <p class="pricing">$3,500</p>
          <p class="timing">fixed · 1 week</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-body">
          <ul>
            <li>Technical feasibility assessment</li>
            <li>Architecture recommendation with trade-offs</li>
            <li>Implementation roadmap with effort estimates</li>
            <li>Go/no-go recommendation with honest reasoning</li>
            <li>Written deliverable you own and keep</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> De-risking an idea before committing real budget.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="https://calendar.app.google/jzac8cPcXKKtnVQ39" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="tier-cta">Book a Discovery Sprint</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-tier">
        <div class="tier-top">
          <h3>Build Sprint</h3>
          <p class="pricing">$6k&ndash;$15k</p>
          <p class="timing">fixed · 2&ndash;6 weeks</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-body">
          <ul>
            <li>End-to-end implementation of a scoped deliverable</li>
            <li>Testing and validation suite</li>
            <li>Documentation and handoff materials</li>
            <li>Weekly progress updates</li>
            <li>2 weeks of bug-fix support after delivery</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Shipping a working feature, integration, or pipeline.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="https://calendar.app.google/jzac8cPcXKKtnVQ39" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="tier-cta">Start a Build Sprint</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-tier">
        <div class="tier-top">
          <h3>Advisory</h3>
          <p class="pricing">$2,000</p>
          <p class="timing">monthly · ongoing</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-body">
          <ul>
            <li>60-minute strategy call each month</li>
            <li>Same-day async responses via message or email</li>
            <li>Architecture and code reviews</li>
            <li>Technical decision-making support</li>
            <li>Priority scheduling when you're ready for a new sprint</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Teams that want ongoing expert guidance between sprints.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="https://calendar.app.google/jzac8cPcXKKtnVQ39" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="tier-cta">Schedule a Call</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="how-it-works">
      <h3>How It Works</h3>
      <p>Go in order, mix and match, or pick just one. Up to you.</p>
      <div class="steps-flow">
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">1</span>
          <strong>Free Consultation</strong>
          <span class="step-desc">You book a free call with us to see if we're a fit.</span>
        </div>
        <span class="step-arrow">→</span>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">2</span>
          <strong>Discovery Sprint</strong>
          <span class="step-desc">We define roadmaps unique to your goals and budget</span>
        </div>
        <span class="step-arrow">→</span>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">3</span>
          <strong>Build Sprint</strong>
          <span class="step-desc">We execute and build something great together</span>
        </div>
        <span class="step-arrow">→</span>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">4</span>
          <strong>Retainer</strong>
          <span class="step-desc">You keep us around for any ongoing support or maintenance</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .packages {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }

  .tiers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .service-tier {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 15px;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .service-tier:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(35, 170, 87, 0.2);
    outline: 2px solid #23aa57;
  }

  .service-tier--free {
  }

  .tier-top {
    padding: 2rem 2rem 1.25rem;
  }

  .service-tier h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .pricing {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #23aa57;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .service-tier--free .pricing {
    color: #23aa57;
  }

  .timing {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #888;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .tier-body {
    padding: 0 2rem 1rem;
    flex: 1;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .service-tier ul {
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .service-tier li {
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-tier li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #23aa57;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .service-tier--free li::before {
    color: #23aa57;
  }

  .best-for {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #555;
    margin: 0;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .tier-cta {
    display: block;
    margin: auto 2rem 2rem;
    padding: 12px 30px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #23aa57 0%, #16a05a 100%);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .tier-cta:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(29, 191, 115, 0.3);
  }

  .service-tier--free .tier-cta {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #23aa57 0%, #16a05a 100%);
  }

  .service-tier--free .tier-cta:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(29, 191, 115, 0.3);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .tiers-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
